name: jschardet

scripts.dist: npm run dist-dev && java -jar node_modules/google-closure-compiler/compiler.jar --warning_level QUIET --compilation_level SIMPLE_OPTIMIZATIONS --js dist/jschardet.js > dist/jschardet.min.js
scripts.dist-dev: mkdir -p dist && browserify index.js -s jschardet --detect-globals false -o dist/jschardet.js
